subject: Basketball
College Athletics
lead_paragraph: DaJuan Summers had 15 points and 9 rebounds, Jonathan Wallace became Georgetown’s career leader in 3-pointers and the seventh-ranked Hoyas (10-1) closed out their non-conference schedule with an 82-55 victory against visiting Fordham on Monday.
